In English and Spanish;
                                    Spanish text not printed. Ratification advised by the Senate,
                                    Jan. 28, 1925; ratified by the President, Apr. 7, 1925;
                                    ratifications deposited with the Government of the United
                                    States, June 13, 1925; proclaimed by the President, June 15,
                                    1925. (Treaty Series No. 717.)
